<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">אזל</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
אזל / 'âzal / aw-zal'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''אזל'''

# To go away, hence to [[disappear]]: - [[fail]], gad about, go to and fro [but in  {{KJVEze|27|19}} the word is rendered by many “from Uzal,” by others “yarn”], be gone (spent).

